<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Cosmosul</title>
    <style>
        /* Stiluri generale*/
        body { text-align: center; font-family: sans-serif; margin: 0; }
        #z1 img { width: 25%; }
        
        #z2 { background: cornflowerblue; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px; }
        #z2 a { background: pink; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 10px; text-decoration: none; color: #000; }
        
        /* Zona de conținut și liste */
        #z3 { font-size: 25px; padding: 20px; }
        .liste { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 50px; text-align: left; font-size: 18px; }
        
        /* Rebus - Tabel centrat cu borduri */
        .rebus { border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px auto; }
        .rebus td { width: 25px; height: 25px; font-size: 20px; }
        .celula { border: 1px solid black; }

        /* Footer cu animație de tip scrolling */
        #z4 { overflow: hidden; white-space: nowrap; }
        #z4 h4 { display: inline-block; animation: miscare 5s linear infinite; }
        @keyframes miscare { 
            from { transform: translateX(-100%); } 
            to { transform: translateX(100%); } 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="z1"><img src="ModelBanner.jpg" alt="Banner"></div>

    <div id="z2">
        <a href="index.html">Cosmosul</a>
        <a href="Explorare.html">Explorarea Spatiala</a>
        <a href="Galerie.html">Galerie foto</a>
    </div>

    <div id="z3">
        <p>Cosmosul este universul văzut ca un sistem ordonat, opusul haosului.</p>
        
        <h3 style="text-align: left;"><b>Cuvinte incrucisate</b></h3>
        <div class="liste">
            <div>
                <ol type="I"><li>Pe orizontala</li></ol>
                <ol><li>Cea mai apropiata planeta de soare</li><li>Planeta cu 27 sateliti</li></ol>
            </div>
            <div>
                <ol type="I" start="2"><li>Pe verticala</li></ol>
                <ol start="3"><li>A doua cea mai mare planeta</li><li>A doua planeta de la Soare</li></ol>
            </div>
        </div>

        <table class="rebus">
            <tr><td></td><td class="celula" style="color:red">S</td></tr>
            <tr style="color: blue;">
                <td class="celula">S</td><td class="celula">O</td><td class="celula">A</td><td class="celula">R</td><td class="celula">E</td>
            </tr>
            <tr><td></td><td class="celula" style="color: green;">L</td></tr>
        </table>

        <video width="30%" controls>
                <source src="Cosmos.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
            <img src="1.jpg" usemap="#poza" width="579px" height="312px">
            <map name="poza">
                    <area shape="circle" coords="231,129,30" href="Jupiter.pdf" alt="Jupiter">
                    <area shape="circle" coords="321,131,30" href="Saturn.pdf" alt="Saturn">
            </map>
    </div>

    <div id="z4"><h4>© ONTI2024–etapa națională</h4></div>
</body>
</html>